        "act": 1,
        "name": "Swims-at-Night",
        "startVideo": "tfh_ch8",
        "endVideo": "tfh_ch8post",
        "startDialogue": "<dl><dd><b>Kellen:</b> <i>\"The cultists kidnapped the sorceress Laaneth, and had taken her north. They would use her to help them bring about a dread prophecy known as The Culling.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Tyr:</b> <i>\"I don't like it any more than you do. But we need a ship to chase the cultists and we don't have any coin. Besides, this ship belongs to smugglers, and I have it on good authority that—\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Swims-at-Night:</b> <i>\"Intruders!\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Tyr:</b> <i>\"... That they're not here tonight.\"</i></dd></dl>",
        "endDialogue": "<dl><dd><b>Kellen:</b> <i>\"The Argonian and the hero realized they had a common enemy. The smuggler, who was called Swims-at-Night, agreed to sail north in search of the sorceress.\"</i></dd></dl>",
