        "act": 2,
        "name": "The Rescue",
        "startVideo": "tfh_ch11",
        "endVideo": "tfh_ch11post",
        "startDialogue": "<dl><dd><b>Kellen:</b> <i>\"The Cultists had taken refuge in an ancient ruin. Only to fall prey to its ferocious new inhabitants.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Tyr:</b> <i>\"Laaneth!\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Laaneth:</b> <i>\"I could use a little help here.\"</i></dd></dl>",
        "endDialogue": "<dl><dd><b>Kellen:</b> <i>\"Laaneth had learned that the cult was secretly led by Lord Naarifin, the Dominion warlord who had captured the Imperial City.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Kellen:</b> <i>\"To bring about the prophecy, he intended to sacrifice all of the city's inhabitants.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Kellen:</b> <i>\"Laaneth suggested they seek out the Imperial Army, then in exile in Skyrim, and warn the emperor of Naarifin's plot.\"</i></dd></dl>",
