        "startDialogue": "<dl><dd><b>Swims-at-Night:</b> <i>\"I don't like these woods.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Tyr:</b> <i>\"This is the shortest way I know to Skyrim.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Laaneth:</b> <i>\"But not the safest.\"</i></dd></dl>",
        "endDialogue": "<dl><dd><b>Kellen:</b> <i>\"In the spider's web, they found a High Elf merchant calling for help.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Isha:</b> <i>\"Did they free him? He might give away their location to the Dominion.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Nagh:</b> <i>\"This one would have taken his gold.\"</i></dd></dl>",
