        "startVideo": "tfh_ch16",
        "endVideo": "tfh_ch16post",
        "startDialogue": "<dl><dd><b>Laaneth:</b> <i>\"Are you sure these crypts will lead us right into the White-Gold Tower?\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Swims-at-Night:</b> <i>\"Are you doubting the greatest smuggler in Tamriel?\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Cassia:</b> <i>\"It's crawling with the undead.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Swims-at-Night:</b> <i>\"Well, if they were safe, everyone would use them.\"</i></dd></dl>",
        "endDialogue": "<dl><dd><b>Kellen:</b> <i>\"Amidst the broken bones of the fallen, the hero spotted an ancient grimoire, filled with the dread secrets of necromancy.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Isha:</b> <i>\"Dared they meddle with such foul magic?\"</i></dd></dl>",
