        "endDialogue": "<dl><dd><b>Healer:</b> <i>\"Thank the Divines. The emperor will live. Thanks to you.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Laaneth:</b> <i>\"He's in no shape to lead the assault.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Emperor:</b> <i>\"No. The troops... must believe the emperor is strong.\"</i></dd>\n<dd><b>Emperor:</b> <i>\"Stranger. You have proven a mighty warrior. Here, take my armor. In my helm, none will know who you are. Lead the battle in my stead. The fate of the Empire is in your hands.\"</i></dd></dl>",
